{"tid":1535290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方：警員執勤時難以分辨真假記者","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:07:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8a6af97f73445709a8ec89215d7a5555840e60","tid":1535290,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方指，6月9日至今共拘捕1140人，包括在昨晚旺角衝突中拘捕23人。對於在清場行動中，警員向記者噴胡椒噴霧，警方指，警員執勤時難以分辨真假記者。<br />\n<br />\n警方星期一晚於旺角警署外驅散示威者，期間一名女子被警員制服後，有警員突然向記者噴胡椒噴霧。警方解釋，是由於有示威者以記者作掩護，企圖襲警及搶犯，又指警員執勤時難以分辨真假記者。<br />\n<br />\n在警員噴胡椒噴霧後，本台攝影師退後與警員保持兩三個身位，繼續拍攝。速龍成員其後趕到，連續推開多名記者，本台攝影師更被推跌受傷。而推跌攝影師的速龍成員身上並沒有展示警員編號，頭盔上的編號部分亦被遮擋。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，案件已接獲投訴，不作評論，但指頭盔上的編號仍然可辨識，承認有關做法不理想。<br />\n<br />\n至於有市民制服後被警員踩手，警方指，警員當時是背向示威者，不揣測是否不小心踩到。"},{"pid":"7c52cfad56289226f7114c5b09ec1e95d1005eaf","tid":1535290,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=361504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361504&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=72dcb79f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361504&h=2371033d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=361504</a>"},{"pid":"8ddfeeb04a30a63f636bd33821ec4e74059a701e","tid":1535290,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa236c44e0e077f824570ecbf57a82a11f33824a","tid":1535290,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a09c306c7a5c7ab843bf1ec75ce9ee1edb0ca4b0","tid":1535290,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iaPLCr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iaPLCr.jpg&h=c969d82e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咪就係因為你地搞撚串個場囉，死黑狗！"},{"pid":"d8bb3cb385036c08f543fd7aca7c065e6ad207f4","tid":1535290,"uid":2373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:55.000Z","msg":"831太子又可以一眼專業判斷邊個係市民邊個係示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7031350d6b675dfab4d5ab2b179a5eee795622e7","tid":1535290,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"即係好快黑警會扮記者打狗？"},{"pid":"76359488ed00b4f80f68504c08ffeaf4ce27a8de","tid":1535290,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"香港理論上唔存在假記者,人人都可以係記者<br />\n呢個係基本法寫明<br />\n除左政府記者會要ON LIST外"},{"pid":"9122b2aada8cde54f7436441128c83b67955db18","tid":1535290,"uid":78046,"lik